that I cancled the post about the force feild plates.

continued to fire at the Destrons.

       The Autoguns, as well as some of the missle turrets fire at the jets 
over head.
       
       The EMP canon sends several shots towrds the Destrons.

       The four manule defense canon fire at the Destrons, the Allience Jets, 
and the other bots.
